OL,6,FBeauty and skincare retailer 'The Body
OL,7,FShop' will close around half of its UK
OL,8,Fstores after going into administration
OL,9,Flast week, with some stores closing on
OL,10,FTuesday
OL,12,Fwill close almost half of its stores,
OL,13,Fwith seven set to shut on Tuesday, the
OL,14,Fcompany's administrators have
OL,15,Fannounced.
OL,17,FThe store has roughly 200 outlets
OL,18,Facross the UK, with over 2,000 staff
OL,19,Ffearing for their jobs, and went into
OL,20,Fadministration last week.
