OL,4,Cits stores
OL,6,FIt will also cut around 270 head
OL,7,Foffice jobs as part of a heavy
OL,8,Frestructuring.
OL,10,FIt comes just weeks after private
OL,11,Fequity firm Aurelius took over the
OL,12,Fbusiness after buying The Body Shop
OL,13,Ffor #207 million in November.
OL,15,FA source close to Aurelius told ITV
OL,16,FNews that The Body Shop sits in a "far
OL,17,Fworse financial state" than it had
OL,18,Fanticipated when it acquired the brand.
