OL,6,FThe retailer was founded in 1976 by
OL,7,FAnita Roddick and her husband Gordon
OL,8,Fas one of the first companies to
OL,9,Fpromote so-called ethical consumerism,
OL,10,Ffocusing on ethically produced
OL,11,Fcosmetics and skincare products.
OL,13,FThe seven Body Shops set to close on
OL,14,FTuesday are:
